<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Daily Habit Check-in</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #4361EE;
      --primary-dark: #3A0CA3;
      --accent: #F72585;
      --light: #F8F9FA;
      --dark: #212529;
      --success: #4CC9F0;
      --gray: #6C757D;
    }
    
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--dark);
      background-color: #f4f5f7;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    .container {
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 30px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    
    .logo h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
      color: var(--dark);
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    
    .logo p {
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .greeting {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 17px;
    }
    
    .habit-box {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--dark);
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .btn-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0;
    }
    
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 15px 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 0 10px;
      border: none;
    }
    
    .btn-yes {
      background-color: #4CC9F0;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-no {
      background-color: #F72585;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .streak-info {
      background-color: var(--light);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    
    .streak-info h3 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 18px;
    }
    
    .streak-info h4 {
      color: var(--dark);
      margin: 15px 0 10px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    .streak-calendar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    
    .day {
      width: 30px;
      height: 30px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      margin-right: 8px;
    }
    
    .day-completed {
      background-color: #4CC9F0;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .day-missed {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      color: var(--gray);
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">
      <h1>18 Day</h1>
      <p>The Habit Launchpad</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="greeting">
      <p>Hi <%= recipientEmail %>,</p>
      <p>Did you complete your daily habit today?</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="habit-box">
      <%= habitDescription %>
    </div>
    
    <div class="btn-container">
      <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/challenge/checkin/<%= challengeId %>/<%= userId %>/yes" style="background-color: #4CC9F0; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;">Yes, I did it!</a>
      <a href="<%= baseUrl %>/challenge/checkin/<%= challengeId %>/<%= userId %>/no" style="background-color: #F72585; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; display: inline-block; margin: 0 10px;">Not today</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="streak-info">
      <h3>Current Streak</h3>
      <p>Your current streak: <strong><%= yourStreak %> days</strong></p>
      <p><%= partnerEmail %>'s current streak: <strong><%= partnerStreak %> days</strong></p>
      
      <h4>Your last 7 days:</h4>
      <div class="streak-calendar">
        <% yourStreakCalendar.forEach(function(day) { %>
          <div class="day <%= day.completed ? 'day-completed' : 'day-missed' %>">
            <%= day.date.split('-')[2] %>
          </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
      
      <h4><%= partnerEmail %>'s last 7 days:</h4>
      <div class="streak-calendar">
        <% partnerStreakCalendar.forEach(function(day) { %>
          <div class="day <%= day.completed ? 'day-completed' : 'day-missed' %>">
            <%= day.date.split('-')[2] %>
          </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <p>Research shows that after 18 days, your brain will have formed new neural pathways, making the habit almost automatic!</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Based on habit formation research by Phillippa Lally et al., UCL</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>